### 주문 생성 (메뉴 기반)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cs/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservationId": 1,
  "note": "덜 맵게요",
  "items": [
    { "menuId": 1, "quantity": 2 },
    { "menuId": 2, "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}

### 관리자 - 주문 목록
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cs/admin/orders

### 관리자 - 준비중 주문만
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cs/admin/orders?status=preparing

### 관리자 - 주문 아이템 보기
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cs/admin/orders/1/items

### 관리자 - 주문 완료 처리
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/cs/admin/orders/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "done"
}

### settings 변경
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/cs/admin/settings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payment": {
    "bankName": "토스뱅크",
    "accountNumber": "123-456"
  }
}
